    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay fine, I'll look for the ibuprofen instead. but i'm honestly running low on that too. if i can't find any, can i just give him a dose of the aspirin and maybe a little bit of his cough syrup? they're both in the cabinet and it seems like a faster way to get him to sleep.",
